                                                      BUSINESS QUESTION
Which group of customers should we target to increase revenue quickly?

                               QUERY
SELECT
CASE
WHEN lifetime_value > 1500 then 'high value customers'
ELSE 'low value customers'
END AS Customers_status,
ROUND(AVG(discount_usage_rate),2) avg_discount,
ROUND(AVG(lifetime_value),2)total_revenue,
ROUND(AVG(total_purchases),2)
FROM ecommerce_data
GROUP BY Customers_status;

                            Insight 
High-value customers generate more revenue, but they are already contributing. There is also an opportunity to grow low-value customers into higher-value customers.

                         Recommendation 
We should maintain strong engagement with high-value customers while also focusing on improving low-value customers through targeted campaigns to increase overall revenue.
